Description: A modular and extensible framework for processing camera-trap
    data and automatically generating reproducible ecological reports. The
    package supports data-quality diagnostics, data manipulation and
    summarisation, ecological analyses, visualisation, and report assembly
    for datasets formatted in, or converted to, the Camtrap-DP standard,
    producing maps, tables, figures, and narrative text to support both
    academic research and wildlife management.
